<title>Game rules</title>
<p>In order to complete the puzzle, you must fill each cell with a number between 1 and 9, inclusive, such that no number is repeated in any row, column or 3x3 box.
</p>
<p>
In a solved sudoku, each row, column, and 3x3 box contains all the numbers 1 through 9.
</p>
<p>
Each puzzle has only one solution.</p>

